Description: The next generation of Yu-Gi-Oh battle it out at the Duel Academy.
Title: YU-GI-OH! GX, VOL. 9
Author: Naoyuki Kageyama

Description: Sailor Moon fights for justice in the name of the Moon and the mysterious Moon Princess. Along the way, she recruits other girls to be Sailor Scouts and join her fight against evil.
Title: SAILOR MOON, VOL. 6
Author: Naoko Takeuchi

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife. In this volume: old alliances are tested.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 44
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife. In this volume: Aizen battles against the greatest captains of the Soul Society.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 45
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: Negi, the boy wizard, learns he will be teaching English at an all-girls high school in Japan, but he must keep his powers a secret.
Title: NEGIMA! MAGISTER NEGI MAGI, VOL. 35
Author: Ken Akamatsu

Description: This series is about grade-school boys who want to become professionals in the manga industry.
Title: BAKUMAN, VOL. 13
Author: Tsugumi Ohba

Description: The Fairy Tail are a group of powerful wizards.
Title: FAIRY TAIL, VOL. 20
Author: Hiro Mashima

Description: From the publisher: "Nanami is shocked to discover that the townsfolk consider her shrine abandoned." Will her work to revitalize the shrine pay off?
Title: KAMISAMA KISS, VOL. 10
Author: Julietta Suzuki

Description: Princess Nakaba and Prince Caesar are married to keep peace between warring countries. Will they learn to love each other?
Title: DAWN OF THE ARCANA, VOL. 5
Author: Rei Toma

Description: Whether rain, shine, sun or snow, the Letter Bee is "entrusted to deliver the hearts of people separated from the ones they love."
Title: TEGAMI BACHI, VOL. 10
Author: Hiroyuki Asada
